<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Xatolik - Blog</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Pro:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #080810 0%, #0f0f1a 100%);
            color: #ccd6f6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #e94560;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #8892b0;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: #c9a227;
            color: #080810;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background: #a88720;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Xatolik yuz berdi</h1>
        <p class="error-message">
            Kechirasiz, kutilmagan xatolik yuz berdi. Iltimos, keyinroq qayta urinib ko'ring.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">
            ← Bosh sahifaga qaytish
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


